Formal Definition "Game"
see https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&source=web&rct=j&opi=89978449&url=https://figshare.mq.edu.au/ndownloader/files/43233216&ved=2ahUKEwja_MO6oqGRAxUj3AIHHYO3KyMQFnoECBoQAQ&usg=AOvVaw2Os6zAf-dm_K-ycXwrZ1lc
- each game state has a function that assigns it its prev. game
- moves are maps from game states to game states
- a strategie is a set of moves closed under itself (oder so)

